　國　　111 　年　　7 　　月　　5 　　日\r\n　　　　　　　　　民事執行處司法事務官　孫家豪","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/KLDV/111%2c%e5%8f%b8%e6%b6%88%e5%82%b5%e8%81%b2%2c3%2c20220705%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"KLDV,111,司消債聲,3,20220705,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"司消債聲","JNO":"3","JDATE":"20220705","JTITLE":"延長履行期限"}